             was indicted for <rs id="t18271025-229-off1316" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18271025-229-off1316" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18271025-229-off1316" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18271025-229-cd1317" type="crimeDate">22d of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271025-229-off1316 t18271025-229-cd1317"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271025-229-off1318 t18271025-229-cd1317"></join>, 4lbs. of tobacco, value 14s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18271025-229-victim1184" type="victimName">
                        Samuel 
                        Fish
                     <interp inst="t18271025-229-victim1184" type="surname" value="Fish"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18271025-229-victim1184" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
